label: uncl9013
comment: Code specifying the reason for a status.

values.label: Address ex delivery area
values.comment: The address for delivery is outside the area of the carrier/transporter.

values.label: After transport departed
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment arrived after the means of transport has departed.

values.label: Agent refusal
values.comment: The agent of the customer refused to accept delivery.

values.label: Altered seals
values.comment: The seals on the equipment have been changed from those notified.

values.label: Appointment scheduled
values.comment: An arrangement has been made to deliver at a specific time.

values.label: Attempt unsuccessful
values.comment: An unsuccessful attempt has been made to deliver the goods/consignments/equipment.

values.label: Business closed
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment could not be delivered/collected as the business was closed.

values.label: Changed schedule
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment cannot/will not be delivered/collected at the arranged time because of a change of schedule.

values.label: Complementary address needed
values.comment: A further address is needed to effect delivery/collection of the goods/consignments/equipment.

values.label: Computer system down
values.comment: The computer system is inoperative.

values.label: Credit approval requested
values.comment: The consignee requests delivery on a credit base.

values.label: Customer arrangements
values.comment: Goods/consignments/equipment require delivery arrangements by the customer.

values.label: Customs refusal
values.comment: The Customs authorities have refused to clear the goods/consignments/equipment.

values.label: Damaged
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment have been damaged.

values.label: Delivery at specific requested dates/times/periods
values.comment: Delivery of the goods/consignments/equipment is requested at specific dates/times/periods.

values.label: Destination incorrect
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment have been sent to wrong destination.

values.label: Departure delay
values.comment: The transport has been delayed in departing on the arranged transport action.

values.label: Derailment
values.comment: The train carrying the goods/consignments/equipment has been derailed.

values.label: Discrepancy
values.comment: There is a discrepancy between the details of goods/ equipment previously provided and the actual situation.

values.label: Dock strike
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment cannot be delivered/collected due to a dock strike.

values.label: Due to customer
values.comment: An action in the transport chain has been affected due to action of the customer.

values.label: Empty
values.comment: The package/equipment is found to be empty.

values.label: Equipment failure
values.comment: Delivery/collection could not be effected due to equipment failure.

values.label: Examination required by relevant authority
values.comment: An examination of the goods/equipment has been ordered by the relevant authority.

values.label: Export restrictions
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment have been prohibited from export pending further investigation.

values.label: Frustrated export
values.comment: Attempts to export the goods/consignments/equipment have been unsuccessful.

values.label: Goods units missing
values.comment: The tally of goods/consignments/equipment does not match the quantity as per advice. Result: less than advised.

values.label: Import restrictions
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment need import checks and tests pending being released for importation.

values.label: Incorrect pick information
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment were not collected due to incorrect pick information.

values.label: Incorrect address
values.comment: The address given for the action was incorrect.

values.label: Industrial dispute
values.comment: The action was frustrated by an industrial dispute.

values.label: Instructions awaited
values.comment: Further instructions are required.

values.label: Lost goods/consignments/equipment
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment have been lost in the course of a movement along the transport chain.

values.label: Means of transport damaged
values.comment: The means of transport on which the goods/consignments/equipment were being (were to be) moved has been damaged.

values.label: Mechanical breakdown
values.comment: There has been a mechanical breakdown of the means of transport/equipment on which the goods/consignments/equipment was being (was to be) moved.

values.label: Mechanical inspection
values.comment: A mechanical inspection of the means of transport/ equipment on which the goods/consignments/equipment were being (were to be) moved, is required.

values.label: Missing and/or incorrect documents
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment require complete and correct documentation.

values.label: New delivery arrangements
values.comment: Alternative delivery arrangements advised by consignee after failed delivery.

values.label: No recipient contact information
values.comment: No information available concerning the responsible person at delivery address.

values.label: Not identified
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment expected to be located and identified in the transport chain cannot be identified.

values.label: Not loaded
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment to be loaded onto a means of transport have not been loaded on the expected transport.

values.label: On deck
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment have been stowed on deck.

values.label: Package not ready
values.comment: The package was not available for collection.

values.label: Package tracking number unknown
values.comment: The package tracking number is unknown.

values.label: Partly missing
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment are partly, but not completely, missing.

values.label: Payment not received
values.comment: The expected payment for the transport action was not received.

values.label: Payment refused
values.comment: The payer refused to pay for the service.

values.label: Plundered
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment have been plundered.

values.label: Refused without reason given
values.comment: The transport action/documentation has been refused without explanation.

values.label: Scheduled past cut-off
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment to be delivered/collected have been scheduled past/later than the cut-off time.

values.label: Shunted to siding
values.comment: The transport on which the goods/consignments/equipment is to be placed has been shunted to siding.

values.label: Signature not required
values.comment: No signature required.

values.label: Sorted wrong route
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment have been sorted erroneously to an incorrect route.

values.label: Special service required
values.comment: A special service is required for the goods/consignments/equipment.

values.label: Split
values.comment: The consignment of goods has been split into two or more consignments.

values.label: Totally missing
values.comment: The total goods/consignments/equipment is missing.

values.label: Tracking information unavailable
values.comment: The tracking information of the goods/consignments/equipment is unavailable.

values.label: Transit delay
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment have been delayed in transit.

values.label: Unable to locate
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment cannot be located.

values.label: Unacceptable condition
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment were in unacceptable condition at time of delivery/collection.

values.label: Under deck
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment have been stowed under/below deck.

values.label: Unknown
values.comment: The reason is unknown.

values.label: Weather conditions
values.comment: The weather conditions have affected collection/delivery.

values.label: Expired free time
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment have been in a storage facility for longer than permitted free time.

values.label: Outstanding claims settled
values.comment: Outstanding claims in respect of goods/consignments/equipment have been settled.

values.label: Stolen
values.comment: A consignment or goods have been stolen.

values.label: Administrative error
values.comment: An administrative error has occurred.

values.label: Undefined incident attributed to buyer
values.comment: An undefined incident has been attributed to the buyer.

values.label: Undefined incident attributed to carrier
values.comment: An undefined incident has been attributed to the carrier.

values.label: Undefined incident attributed to logistic service provider
values.comment: An undefined incident has been attributed to the logistic service provider.

values.label: Change in agreed product reference
values.comment: An agreed reference associated with a product has changed.

values.label: Difference in replenishment figures
values.comment: A difference has been identified between the opening inventory balance, the physical count of incoming replenishment inventory, and the closing inventory balance.

values.label: Lost quantity of variable measurement product
values.comment: A quantity of a variable measurement product which has been lost.

values.label: Damaged during manipulation in warehouse
values.comment: Product damaged during the manipulation process in a warehouse.

values.label: Product degenerated during storage or transport
values.comment: A product has degenerated during storage or transport.

values.label: Destroyed
values.comment: The goods, consignments, or equipment have been destroyed.

values.label: Best before date expired
values.comment: A product's best before date has expired.

values.label: Log number assignment
values.comment: Log number is assigned.

values.label: Entry point assessment of Data Maintenance Request (DMR) initial comment
values.comment: An entry point is providing its initial comments on a DMR.

values.label: Entry point assessment of Data Maintenance Request (DMR) latest comment
values.comment: An entry point is providing its latest comments on a DMR.

values.label: Unable to take corrective action
values.comment: Corrective action could not be taken.

values.label: International assessment group reporting on Data Maintenance Request (DMR)
values.comment: The international assessment group has determined if the Data Maintenance Request (DMR) is to be included in the next publication of the standard.

values.label: Missing
values.comment: Specified goods/consignments/equipment are missing.

values.label: Central secretariat review cycle start
values.comment: Report start of the central secretariat review cycle.

values.label: Data structure tag assigned
values.comment: A data structure has been assigned a permanent tag.

values.label: Non-operational periods
values.comment: Waiting due to being outside the period of operation.

values.label: Error
values.comment: Information is in error.

values.label: Accident involving means of transport
values.comment: The means of transport being used to move the consignment has been involved in an accident.

values.label: Order or instruction status change
values.comment: A status of an order or instruction has changed.

values.label: Not accepted by delivery party
values.comment: The delivery was not accepted by the delivery party.

values.label: Delivery requested to another location by ordering party
values.comment: Goods have been delivered to another location following an instruction from the ordering party.

values.label: Incorrect goods delivered
values.comment: The goods delivered were incorrect.

values.label: Undefined incident attributed to customs authority
values.comment: An undefined incident has been attributed to the customs authority.

values.label: Imperfect item
values.comment: Item has defect(s).

values.label: Excess goods delivered
values.comment: Excess goods have been delivered.

values.label: Goods partially delivered
values.comment: Goods were partially delivered.

values.label: Remove to federal court
values.comment: Action has been removed to a federal court level.

values.label: Change of venue granted
values.comment: A change in venue has been approved.

values.label: Replenish inventory
values.comment: The goods, consignment and/or equipment have replenished inventory.

values.label: Unloading date and or time not received
values.comment: The unloading date and or time was not received.

values.label: Stacked pallets not acceptable
values.comment: Stacked pallets are not accepted by the goods recipient.

values.label: Pallets containing mixed goods not acceptable
values.comment: Pallets containing mixed goods are not accepted by goods recipient.

values.label: Product expiry date not acceptable
values.comment: The product expiry date is not accepted.

values.label: Pallet and goods height higher than permitted
values.comment: The combined height of the pallet and goods is higher than permitted.

values.label: Delivery order not received
values.comment: The delivery order was not received.

values.label: Back-orders not permitted by goods recipient
values.comment: Back-orders are not permitted by the goods recipient.

values.label: Article identification not found in computer system
values.comment: Article identification is not found in computer system.

values.label: Goods not barcoded
values.comment: Goods are not barcoded.

values.label: Delivered later than scheduled date/time
values.comment: Delivery has taken place later than the scheduled date/time.

values.label: Delivery different date
values.comment: Delivery will, or has, taken place on a date different to that requested on the order.

values.label: Delayed due to various reasons
values.comment: Standing over due to various reasons.

values.label: Goods previously delivered
values.comment: Delivery of goods has already taken place.

values.label: Loading error
values.comment: An error while loading the order or goods has occured, e.g. wrong goods, wrong transport equipment, wrong mode of transport, etc.

values.label: Delivery too late
values.comment: A delivery of an order or goods has been refused because it has arrived late.

values.label: Partial delivery not accepted
values.comment: A partial delivery of an order has not been accepted by the ordering party.

values.label: Unloading of goods delayed
values.comment: The unloading of goods at the point of delivery has been delayed by the carrier for no specific reason.

values.label: Product out of stock
values.comment: An order for a specific product can not be fulfilled currently because the product is out of stock.

values.label: Incident attributed to seller
values.comment: An undefined incident has been attributed to the seller.

values.label: Incident not attributed
values.comment: An undefined incident has not been attributed to any party.

values.label: Manufacturing defects
values.comment: Items received have manufacturing defects which make them unacceptable.

values.label: Other
values.comment: An other incident (undefined) has occured.

values.label: Monetary amount error
values.comment: The reason for an error is an error concerning the monetary amount.

values.label: Product not ordered
values.comment: The reason for an error is a product was not ordered.

values.label: Product not accepted
values.comment: A product was delivered which was not accepted by the delivery party.

values.label: Despatch preparation error
values.comment: The error was caused because of an error in the preparation of the despatch.

values.label: Inventory differences
values.comment: Differences in inventory detected when carrying out a physical inventory count.

values.label: Physical movement between warehouses
values.comment: A difference in inventory due to physical movement between warehouses.

values.label: Manipulation
values.comment: A difference in inventory due to the physical manipulation of goods.

values.label: Importation
values.comment: A difference in inventory due to the addition of imported goods to inventory.

values.label: Delivery party premise closed during normal hours
values.comment: The premises of the delivery party were closed during normal hours.

values.label: Delivery incomplete - time shortage at delivery location
values.comment: The carrier was unable to complete the delivery of goods due to a shortage of time at the delivery location to handle the delivery.

values.label: Delivery party premise closed for stock taking
values.comment: The premises of the delivery party were closed because of stock taking.

values.label: Delivery party premise closed on Saturday
values.comment: The premises of the delivery party were closed on Saturday.

values.label: Delivery party premise closed on national holiday
values.comment: The premises of the delivery party were closed on a national holiday.

values.label: Postponed delivery
values.comment: Temporary refusal of a part or of the whole delivery.

values.label: After action taken by logistics service provider
values.comment: After an action was taken on the goods/consignments/equipment by the logistics service provider.

values.label: Logistics service provider following instructions by owner
values.comment: Action taken by the logistics service provider on goods/consignments/equipment as instructed by owner.

values.label: Arrived
values.comment: The goods/consignments/equipment/means of transport has arrived at a location.

values.label: Expiration of sales period
values.comment: Goods' sales period has expired.

values.label: Awaiting release
values.comment: Goods are on hold awaiting release.

values.label: Quality control held
values.comment: Goods held from distribution waiting for the outcome of a quality control assessment.

values.label: Incident attributed to despatch party
values.comment: Incident has been attributed to the despatch party.
